{"tid":1235983,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《食戟之靈》動畫四期製作確定 2019 年 10 月起開播","createTime":"2019-06-17T10:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T12:55:51.000Z","uid":34999,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"90c3f5bc13dea647d54dd3b8a4b00a3fc6b42e67","tid":1235983,"uid":34999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:06:47.000Z","msg":"由 附田祐斗 擔任原作、佐伯俊 所繪製的料理漫畫《食戟之靈》，就在 6 月 17 日所發行的「週刊少年Jump 29 號」正式迎向最終回。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　《食戟之靈》是一部描述著家裡經營餐館的中學生．幸平創真，進到「遠月學園」就讀並有所成長的料理戰鬥漫畫。在料理研究家的 森崎友紀 的幫助下，自 2012 年起連載至今，漫畫單行本目前發行至 35 集。<br />\n<br />\n　　此外，也正式確定本作電視動畫第四期《食戟之靈 神之皿》，也將自 2019 年 10 月起開始播放。就在最新一期的「週刊少年Jump 29 號」上釋出有創與繪里奈圖案的最新視覺圖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　還有，自 6 月 27 日起連續三個月所發行的「少年Jump GIGA 2019 SUMMER」也將連續刊登漫畫的篇章《食戟之靈～Le dessert～》。而且「少年Jump GIGA 2019 SUMMER」也將連續三期將會是《食戟之靈》與 Jump 作品的聯名封面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=181221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fgnn%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D181221&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=6ed5cc4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=181221</a>"},{"pid":"cd031dbcb63f1543afd78b14b652fe878d40db5c","tid":1235983,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5663dcd2553b122a6f1b05e3d310725dd0f47f16","tid":1235983,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢套垃圾"},{"pid":"e814974b9ad1278c979828c9ee53300b916999c6","tid":1235983,"uid":204917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:55:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}